Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Opening Skit ===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, you've really become reliable lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:08.84,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:12.42,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It seems my sister trusts Mei-senpai quite a bit as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.80,3,host,0,0,0,,Na-Natsumi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.58,3,host,0,0,0,,It really doesn't look that way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I feel like Mei-chan naturally leads all the 1st and 2nd years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,or gives them a push when they need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Just as Kanon-senpai says, Mei-senpai takes the initiative to keep everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.68,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:35.06,3,host,0,0,0,,If I don't do it, everyone just does whatever they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:36.08,3,host,0,0,0,,so I don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you can step up without hesitating like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:44.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd just leave the leading to Chi-chan or Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.90,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-senpai was also very reliable when we were heading to Music World."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.14,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Oh, I heard about that from Margarete-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You did a great job, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.56,3,host,0,0,0,,Back then, I just thought I wanted to be a bit more like Chisato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:00:59.73,3,host,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.66,3,host,0,0,0,,looking back now, I think I was a bit too tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.08,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I think that's perfectly fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:11.83,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing Mei-senpai work hard has the benefit of making Liella more positive."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:12.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It makes us feel like we can't afford to lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.43,3,host,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.48,3,host,0,0,0,,You and the others, Kanon-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.88,3,host,0,0,0,,No, no, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.20,3,host,0,0,0,,There's no way you seniors would lose to someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You just said "someone like me," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:33.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You have more power to move those around you than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Plus, you have the kindness to support others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.41,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.44,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Margarete says that often too."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.37,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I can't afford to lose to Mei-senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.01,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Or so she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.84,3,host,0,0,0,,I can definitely imagine her saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.42,3,host,0,0,0,,By the way, your Margarete impression is spot on, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.56,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm flattered."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Anyway, Mei-chan, you're the driving force of Liella,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so I'm counting on you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.52,3,host,0,0,0,,Driving force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.36,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that might be a bit of an exaggeration...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.20,3,host,0,0,0,,But fine, if it's just lighting a fire under the engine, I'll do it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's very reassuring."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:15.38,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"In that case, please go ahead and light a fire under my sister's motivation for the next exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.07,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.69,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Then light a fire under my baking, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.60,3,host,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.28,3,host,0,0,0,,I can't look after you that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:43.12,4,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' High School Broadcasting Station: Lieraji - Tomari, Kanon, and Mei!
Comment: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm Date Sayuri, the voice of Kanon Shibuya."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm Sakakura Sakura, also known as Sakuchan, the voice of Tomari Onitsuka."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,And I'm Yabushima Akane, also known as Yabuchan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"the voice of Mei Yoneme."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Together, we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.08,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's a pleasure to be here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.43,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So, this time we're bringing you the trio of Tomari, Kanon, and Mei."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan's here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Let's do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.35,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Glad to have you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.57,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thanks for having me."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:25.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Today is March 24th, but coming up on March 28th, which is Sunny Pa Day..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:30.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's the birthday of Hijirisawa Yuna's voice actress, Yoshitake-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Happy birthday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Sunny Pa Day really is Sunny Pa Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right? It's too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:37.75,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is. Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Let's all celebrate when the day comes."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.37,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:42.93,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're counting on you."
Comment: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Suggestion Box ===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Now then, we've received some mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's from Liella name: Kabo-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.16,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.61,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on being confirmed to perform at LuckyFes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.17,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing Liella perform in Ibaraki, the hometown of the Onitsuka sisters and myself, was one of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So when I saw the announcement, my emotions exploded so much I almost screamed out loud at work!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Hitachi Seaside Park is a place where I have so many memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:22.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,like going on school trips as a kid or having barbecues with my family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:27.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm so happy to be able to make new memories there with everyone in Liella."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:27.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm really looking forward to having the best time with Liella again this summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.68,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next is Liella name: Takashi from Sendai. Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on your appearance at LuckyFes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.27,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it's a festival in Ibaraki, the home of the Onitsuka sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.39,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm sure it'll feel extra special."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:57.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's a summer festival, so please sweep the venue into a whirlwind of excitement with your hot performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:57.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Also, I'm looking forward to seeing if you'll perform any songs that scream "summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Definitely. They also said, "I'd love to hear about your enthusiasm for the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:09.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,or if there's anything specific you're hoping to do at a summer fest!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.90,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's right, Liella will be appearing on Day 2 of LuckyFes, on the 9th."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.40,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's officially decided!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're performing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm so happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's great that it's in Ibaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Since it's the Onitsuka sisters' hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we've always wanted to perform in Ibaraki someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy it's coming true! And the other artists are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:45.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.89,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:51.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll give it our all to show Liella!'s power and keep up with everyone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're looking forward to it."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please look forward to it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It'll be the middle of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,August 8th and 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Make sure to keep your strength up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and come see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:00.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Bring sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:02.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Bring sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, are we performing while holding sports drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.95,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Maybe we should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The liquid might go flying everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Go flying, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.59,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That'd be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'd be all sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's gonna be so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please come see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll be waiting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.62,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Alright, please stay with us until the very end!"
Comment: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:28.60,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:28.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station: Liella! Let's Superstar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.48,4,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station: Liella!"
