Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.50,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's time for the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Suggestion Box, where we read your letters."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Alright everyone, let's say it together! Ready, set... Suggestion Box!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Okay, let's get to the mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This first one is from Liella name: Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:01.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I attended both days of the 7th Live in Kanagawa and watched the Aichi performance via stream."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:07.45,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-chan's solo song, 'Sky Linker,' started with her taking the baton from the club president, Chisato-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.48,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"What was especially memorable was the part at the end of the chorus where she thrusts her fist forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.15,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:18.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it happened several times during the song, the first time I saw it, I was moved to tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and from the second time onwards, I was thrusting my fist right along with her."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.43,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was a performance where I felt the full extent of Mei-chan's straightforward strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:29.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"encompassing her big heart, her kindness that embraces weakness, and her desire to protect. That's what they wrote."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.64,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.78,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next is from Liella name: Baron Ojipan."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Regarding 'Sky Linker,' the clapping with hands near the face during the instrumental break,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:43.94,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and the side steps that followed, looked like a traditional Spanish dance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"like Flamenco."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yeah."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Spain is often called the land of passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and I felt like the dance expressed the passion Mei-chan hides within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The moment I first saw it, I thought, 'Whoa, that's so cool!'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And with that... Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's 'goodbye' in Spanish. (Laughs) That's the letter."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ciao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Alright, next is from Liella name: Red-haired Kana. Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seeing 'Sky Linker' on Day 1 of the 7th Live in Kanagawa was truly the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yabu-chan's dance was so cool I couldn't get it out of my head,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and it still leaves a strong impression on me now."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:20.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The song and lyrics are great, and I listen to it all the time."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'd love to see the 'Sky Linker' dance again somewhere! That's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.83,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Wow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.84,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,I want to hear more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.98,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"'Sky Linker' was seriously so cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.65,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.21,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,At first, I wondered if she'd perform with a mic stand, just standing there and hyping up the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't really imagine her doing an intense dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:41.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:52.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I kept wondering how it would turn out, but I never expected Flamenco in the instrumental break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:52.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, it was a really valuable experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's not every day you get to do Flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:02.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the video of Mei-chan's choreography,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, 'What kind of dance is this?!'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.69,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan was doing a style of dance that none of us had ever done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I told her, 'Wow, this is amazing!' and when I heard it was Flamenco, I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:16.54,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, 'How do you even do that?'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it at all at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:29.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No way, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:33.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It used a core that I'd never used before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The whole foundation of the movement was completely different. I don't know much about dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but even I could tell it was incredibly difficult and confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mhm, mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:42.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I practiced that instrumental break over and over again at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But you were so good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:50.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It makes me nervous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:57.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since everyone does their solo choreography lessons separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we don't even know when the others are practicing, or even...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,what they're doing in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:08.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So when I finally saw it, I was like, 'Whoa, she's doing Flamenco!'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was such a shock.
Comment: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:17.12,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:17.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We didn't really know if each other's songs would have dancing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, when I met up with the other members, I'd be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,'Wait, are you dancing to Kanon-chan's song?'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,or 'How much dancing is there?'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We had conversations like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:32.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Then I happened to run into Yabu right after she finished Mei-chan's choreography lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:38.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She muttered something like, 'It was kind of flamenco-ish...'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And I was like, 'Wait, what do you mean?' I was so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I just couldn't wrap my head around the word 'flamenco'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Yabu said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I pictured her standing tall at a mic stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,with a fiery vibe. So when I heard 'flamenco'...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:02.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't really get many chances to see flamenco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's not something Liella would usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All of us doing flamenco together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:12.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It must be hard when you don't even know what the 'right' way to do it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It looks difficult just watching it, so I think it would've been really tough to actually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's incredibly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I saw how much you were practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, your moves were so sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:34.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Miku-san said, that part where you thrust your fist forward feels so direct and so much like Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:42.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's technically a dance move, but it doesn't feel like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:40.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It feels like you're putting your whole heart into that fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:54.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I found myself getting really emotional during that part too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That happens at the end of the first chorus, right? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The end of the second chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And you do it in the final chorus too, so it's the very last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The movement is the same every time, but for the first,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:13.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,second, and final time, the feelings behind it felt different to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:20.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Depending on the performance, what I'm feeling in that moment changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,so I put all those emotions into my fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I also really love the sound of the glass shattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That part is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:31.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:35.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can hear it even better during the live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:40.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really resonated. And the flames in the background...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,matched Mei-chan so well, it was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And since 'Fanatic' was right after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:53.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were getting ready, so we were watching Mei-chan from the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:57.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Feeling that heat, the two of us were like, 'Alright, let's go!'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We felt like we had to keep that momentum going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was really, really great."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.34,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Can I say something too? Kanon performs before Mei-chan,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.66,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and then there's a bit of time before Kanon's next turn."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:19.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So I was able to watch Mei-chan as she was about to go on stage."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"From backstage, you know."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And of course, before that too,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:31.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but I'd also see Mei-chan—I mean, Yabu—right after her performance."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:38.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Every time she finished, she had this look of passionate fulfillment,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but at the same time, she always looked like she was thinking,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,'What should I do next?' She always had that expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yabu did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, how do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She had her own sense of accomplishment from giving it her all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but she also looked like she felt she still had a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And that just felt so much like Mei-chan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was almost in tears while drinking my hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Just watching her."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's so Mei-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"From our perspective, it was already so wonderful."
Comment: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's going through it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like, what... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your own what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The wall is so high... no, no, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone has such high aspirations and we all think that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:38.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's why I feel like I have to work harder too, being inspired by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I might not have felt that way if I were alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but seeing and feeling everyone's performance made me think I could go further,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:51.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and that there's more I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The solo songs this time really were a source of mutual inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Me too, everyone was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was really happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mutually, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:11.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though a solo song is for one person, I felt like I wasn't alone during those performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I felt like we were all building it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and the costumes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That "Girl Crush" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,These are so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I've never worn anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:28.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you told me they were private clothes, they'd be the most like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They wouldn't look out of place walking around a stylish town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Some people probably wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The fishnet tights were wonderful."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That was a first for me in my life."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Fishnet tights...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is it okay for people to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm just full of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.83,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were worshipping them backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I definitely was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:50.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was worshipping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and on the final day, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:59.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,During one of the last shows, it wasn't part of the choreo, but her hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:04.34,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,got in her face, and while looking forward or casting her eyes down—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I forget which, but she brushed it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and the camera caught it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That part was just too good, like, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I would definitely put that on repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ah, the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you, hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was seriously so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "Whoa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.87,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san doesn't remember it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san doesn't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But it was so beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I loved it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:32.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:34.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I bet some people are saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Please remember it, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next, we have a message from Liella name: Hajiketa Kata Popcorn."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 7th Live."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That was tough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All the 2nd and 3rd years were saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:18.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but the choreography was really, really difficult. And yet, to the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it's a kind of difficulty that's hard to imagine. From their perspective, it looks like we're having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:29.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and the dancing looks effortless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it was actually really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yeah, it was truly difficult."
Comment: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yeah, when we first learned the choreo, we all felt like our souls were leaving our bodies."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:19:05.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We were all so worried about whether we could actually sing and dance it at the same time, but the more we practiced, the more our breathing synced up. Eventually, that anxiety turned into pure fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:19.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So on the day of the live, I felt more of a sense of unity with the audience than worry. How about you guys?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:18.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right. Ever since "High Motivation" was announced...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:35.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...everyone was so excited to see the performance. I felt a lot of pressure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:44.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I also thought the choreo would be a bit simpler, or maybe have a "sweeter" feel to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But it's a lot of dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Why is it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:20:07.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was worried we wouldn't be able to express the fun of the song, but as the live got closer, our practice gave us confidence. We decided to just have fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:57.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:18.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...and show everyone that the 2nd and 3rd gen members can do this! We wanted to deliver that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:31.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,In the end, we had fun, but at first, we couldn't even think about that. We were just desperate. When we first tried singing and dancing together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:28.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:37.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...we were all like, "This is impossible! This is really bad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:48.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though there are fewer of us than the full 11, we couldn't even catch our breath. The formations were so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:55.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And the rhythm isn't just a simple 1-2-3-4 beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:21:03.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's like, "Wait, we're dancing to those tiny little sounds too?" The choreographer really packed it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was something. But it turned out great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,What part was especially difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,From our perspective watching you, like Saku said, you're hitting every single beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:24.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But since we're just watching, we just end up thinking, "Wow, that looks like fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:25.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, where was the struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,With other songs, I can usually point to one specific part that was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:38.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But with this one, every single part was a little bit difficult, so it felt hard the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:38.93,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was just... tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:46.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How do I put it? Usually, when it's not your turn to sing, you might just be standing there watching the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But there's almost none of that in this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You're always doing one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:22:00.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You're constantly moving, and the formations are tough. You just end up totally out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.45,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I can say it now, but I was a mess during the choreo lessons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:09.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:12.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone was basically crying while doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:13.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was crying my eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really wondered what was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"What's going to happen to us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I thought, "Mei-chan would never cry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:20.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:28.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...so seeing her cry made me cry even more. I don't even know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:27.71,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I can talk about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:43.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone practiced so much at home. When we met up again, the quality had improved so much. I was so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, the lyrics even say something about "having changed," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Hearing this story makes me think that's exactly what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I wasn't there since I'm a 1st gen member, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:58.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Even the title is "High Motivation.""
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:22:59.79,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,During rehearsals, the 2nd and 3rd gens would be like, "Alright!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:08.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,"High Motivation!" they'd say, pumping themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing that just made me think, "That's so cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:18.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really can't get through a song like that without that kind of motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But during the actual performance, everyone looked so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:30.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You were all smiling, so I realized how much hard work must have gone into getting to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Because everyone gave it their all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.50,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,By the way, did you see Nako's impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Eh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You haven't seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.55,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You should have her show you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:39.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Did you take a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, I didn't, but she's always mimicking the "High Motivation" choreo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:49.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so incredibly cute, so you should definitely ask Nako to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:49.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She mimics a very specific part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:52.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:53.47,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I've gotta see that.
Comment: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what is it? What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:58.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:03.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Alright, we've talked a lot, but we're not quite finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:06.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"so we'll keep the conversation going next week."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:07.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.90,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Anyway, thank you all so much for all the emails."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:11.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Comment: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:15.47,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Lunchtime Request ===
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:15.47,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Now, let's read a mail for our Lunchtime Request segment."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's from Radio name: Mizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:19.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.96,0:24:21.10,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'd like to request 'Sky Linker'."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:28.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"My favorite part of this song is definitely right before the final chorus,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"during the 'Right now, I'll change it' part."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:35.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-chan usually has a lower voice, but she hits a clear high note there,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.98,0:24:40.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and I just love the gap and her soulful, scream-like singing voice."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.12,Date Sayuri,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:43.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.72,0:24:46.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel the soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:59.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's a very passionate song, so I hope you'll listen closely to the vocals and the backing track as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.82,0:25:03.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yoneme Mei, "Sky Linker."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.16,0:25:10.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,The reason you only notice the missing pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:18.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,is because you know what perfection looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:21.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:28.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'm far from a god who can end someone's hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:36.40,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,but I'll stay in the rain with you until we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:42.36,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,My wish is in the blue sky, I'll take the hand that reaches for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:47.74,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll block out everything, yes, everything that's hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.74,0:25:50.68,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:52.67,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:58.60,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, don't lose to this depressing world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:26:00.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:14.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,and fly over the many obstacles to reach our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,We've become what you call comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:29.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,When I pray for someone other than myself, I'll prove there's not a single cloud of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:35.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Dive into the blue sky; if you hold this hand, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:37.79,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything—what's wrong with being weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:44.16,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want to cry, let's cry and scream, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.18,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:50.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, I'll accept any version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:51.88,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:20.92,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Even if you're cracked, I'll show you I can take it all without breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:32.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want a tough vessel, if you want a clear present, I'll change it for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.80,0:27:34.04,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,In that blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:37.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,if you look up, I'll take you into the brilliant blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:39.31,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:42.56,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything that's hazy, I'll block it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:45.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:51.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll support you; you have a place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:53.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Don't lose, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station, Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:13.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Radio.
Comment: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Closing ===
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,News from Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.24,0:28:21.42,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Here is the music information."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"On Wednesday, July 8th, the release of the Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Musubu Project mini-album has been confirmed."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:34.82,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We will release five versions: Original, Photo, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.82,0:28:41.94,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Original, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green versions feature new illustrations,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:45.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"while the Photo version uses new photos of the cast."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:52.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It will include 4 songs, including one new group track, plus off-vocal versions for a total of 8 tracks."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:56.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"As a first-press bonus, the Original, Team Kids,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.76,0:29:00.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Team Sports, and Team Green versions will include member stickers."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Photo version will include a purikura-style sticker."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:08.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"All versions will include an advance lottery application ticket for the Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.10,0:29:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Love Live! Superstar!!."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Additionally, as a bundle purchase bonus, we'll be giving away"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"a Liella! sticker book."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:17.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,To celebrate the release of the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:24.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Musubu Project mini-album, we've decided to hold a handover event."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:29.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The dates are Friday, October 2nd, and Friday, October 9th."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Those who pre-order or purchase the Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:38.40,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Musubu Project mini-album at participating stores will be invited to the handover event via lottery."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:45.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The cast members vary by date, so please check the application guidelines before applying."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:49.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Check the Love Live! Superstar!! official website for details."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.68,0:29:53.83,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"News from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The Start Deck "Love Live! Superstar!!",
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:30:02.78,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"featuring only Liella! members and songs, will be released on Saturday, May 30th."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:08.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This product will include a special rarity "Secret Serial" card with a serial number."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:13.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Each numbered card is a super-luxurious, one-of-a-kind item in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.44,0:30:24.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Start Deck allows you to play LoveCa! immediately, so even if you haven't played before, please pick this up and get started."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:32.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Latest info will be posted on the Love Live! official site and X, so keep an eye out."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:34.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Appearance information."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:35.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Starting April 1st, Liella!'s"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:36.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"ChuChu Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.68,0:30:38.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Season 2 will begin on Nippon TV."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.16,0:30:43.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Panshin No. 3 will continue as the program MC from Season 1."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:48.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and Nittele TADA after the broadcast."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:54.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Furthermore, to commemorate the broadcast, the live event "Love Live! Superstar!! Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,no ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:31:02.34,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"2026" will be held at LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY on August 1st and 2nd."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.34,0:31:10.02,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Official secondary lottery applications are open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, April 5th."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.02,0:31:11.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please check this out as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.44,0:31:16.74,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"For details on all the information announced today, please check the Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:21.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"official X account and the Love Live! Superstar!! official website."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's all for the announcements."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.16,0:31:35.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station, Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye to the radio show.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Here is some information about our upcoming broadcasts."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:51.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Episode 266, scheduled for Tuesday, March 31st, will once again feature Yabushima Akane, the voice of Mei Yoneme."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:32:02.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And for Episode 267 on Tuesday, April 7th, we'll have Ookuma Wakana, the voice of Kinako Wakana, for a Toma-Kano-Shiki episode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.22,0:32:04.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're looking forward to your messages!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:07.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So, how did you enjoy today's broadcast?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.80,0:32:08.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.44,0:32:10.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:11.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:13.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, is it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.89,0:32:15.39,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:19.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:21.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura, you surprised me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.84,0:32:23.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to join in on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:26.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "When did Sakura become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:27.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,They're worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:33.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of a comeback, so I figured I'd just join in instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:32.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:34.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.88,0:32:37.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabushima looked so confused just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura, they're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Being pitied is the most embarrassing thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, how was it for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.26,0:32:49.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I got to share my thoughts in such great detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:51.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I mean, I talked quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:52.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Was that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:53.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.92,0:32:55.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone wanted to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:57.99,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'll be talking more next week, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.99,0:32:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.56,0:33:02.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder how long we can keep talking about the 5th Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:05.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We're planning to talk about it for about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.62,0:33:06.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Roughly that long, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We'll keep going until we've covered every single song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:08.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, then let's do every song!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.52,0:33:10.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We won't be able to start the Unit Live at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.56,0:33:12.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I don't know about that."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.26,0:33:12.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll push it back."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.84,0:33:13.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll push it back! We'll push it back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:19.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And with that, this has been Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:20.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's all for this episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri, the voice of Shibuya Kanon,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:24.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:26.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Yabushima Akane, the voice of Yoneme Mei."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:36.64,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,"Because I heard a \"see you\" in the breathtaking sunset."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,"The breeze and you."
